# 📊 PRODEV - Developer Project Management System

Aplikasi Windows Forms untuk tracking developer dan project performance dengan PostgreSQL database.

---

## 🎯 Project Overview

**PRODEV** adalah platform management yang dirancang untuk:
- 👨‍💻 Manage data developer (nama, project, contract status)
- 📈 Track performance metrics (fitur selesai, bug count)
- 📊 Visualisasi performa dalam DataGridView
- 💾 Persistent data dengan PostgreSQL database
- 🔐 Encapsulation & Inheritance dalam OOP design

---

## 📁 Project Structure

```
Responsi2/
├── Models/
│   ├── BaseEntity.cs          # Abstract base class
│   ├── Developer.cs         # Developer model with encapsulation
│   └── Performance.cs       # Performance model
├── Services/
│   └── DeveloperService.cs    # Business logic layer
├── Data/
│   ├── DatabaseConnection.cs  # Database connection manager
│   ├── DeveloperRepository.cs  # Developer CRUD operations
│   └── PerformanceRepository.cs # Performance CRUD operations
├── Configuration/
│   └── DatabaseConfigHelper.cs # Config helper utilities
├── Database/
│   └── schema.sql     # PostgreSQL schema
├── Form1.cs    # Main UI
├── Form1.Designer.cs          # UI design
├── DatabaseSetupForm.cs       # DB config form
├── appsettings.json      # Configuration
├── QUICKSTART.md     # Quick setup guide
└── DATABASE_SETUP.md       # Detailed setup guide
```

---

## 🔧 Technology Stack

- **Language**: C# 13.0
- **Framework**: .NET 9 Windows Forms
- **Database**: PostgreSQL
- **Driver**: Npgsql 10.0.0
- **Architecture**: Repository Pattern + Service Layer

---

## 🏗️ Architecture Diagram

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Form1 (UI Layer)              │
│  ┌──────────────────────────────────┐   │
│  │ - Buttons (Insert, Update, Delete)   │
│  │ - TextBoxes (Input)       │
│  │ - DataGridView (Display)           │
│  └──────────────────────────────────┘   │
└─────────────────────────────────────────┘
              ↓
┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│   DeveloperService (Business Logic) │
│  ┌──────────────────────────────────┐   │
│  │ - AddDeveloper()    │
│  │ - UpdateDeveloper()               │
│  │ - DeleteDeveloper()   │
│  │ - GetAllDevelopers()    │
│  └──────────────────────────────────┘   │
└─────────────────────────────────────────┘
        ↓
┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│        Repository Layer (Data Access)    │
│  ┌──────────────────────────────────┐   │
│  │ DeveloperRepository           │   │
│  │ PerformanceRepository      │   │
│  └──────────────────────────────────┘   │
└─────────────────────────────────────────┘
       ↓
┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│    DatabaseConnection (Npgsql)          │
│  ┌──────────────────────────────────┐   │
│  │ PostgreSQL Database   │   │
│  │ (prodev_db)            │   │
│  └──────────────────────────────────┘   │
└─────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

