## 🎓 Learning Points

Project ini mengimplementasikan:
- ✅ **OOP Principles**: Encapsulation, Inheritance, Abstraction
- ✅ **Design Patterns**: Repository Pattern, Service Layer
- ✅ **Async Programming**: async/await dengan Npgsql
- ✅ **Database Design**: PostgreSQL schema dengan FK & indexes
- ✅ **Windows Forms**: UI with DataGridView, TextBoxes, ComboBoxes
- ✅ **Configuration Management**: appsettings.json handling
- ✅ **Error Handling**: Try-catch, validation, user feedback

